text: Beisel may refer to: * Beisel (car), a 1914 cyclecar manufactured in Monroe, Michigan * Beisel-Mitchell House, a historic house in Paragould, Arkansas ==People== * Christian Beisel (born 1982), German football player * Elizabeth Beisel (born 1992), American competition swimmer * Monty Beisel (born 1978), American football player * Rex Beisel (1893–1972), American aeronautical engineer and pioneer in the science and industry of aviation
